metadata.name: SEED THREE (i)
metadata.description:
Damien Roach
SEED THREE, 2022
Unique animation and sound, NFT 
1920x1920
55s duration 
Series of 55

A series of 55 unique animated NFTs each with a unique audio track.
 
Each animation is unique and accompanied by its own individual, mutated reworking of the 5 classical compositions from SEED TWO. The facsimile tuning orchestra now fragmented and processed into a glowing, hi-tech, prismatic ambience. When played alongside the other 55 animations infinite new musical variations may be created.
